data.text:
BEFORE and after she transitioned, Caitlyn has been in three marriages during her career.

Her current partner reportedly claims that their relationship is more of a business partnership than a romantic relationship.

Who is Caitlyn Jenner dating?

As of the time of writing, Caitlyn Jenner is reportedly dating Sophia Hutchins.

The pair became friends when Caitlyn transitioned in 2015, and rumors went wild about their romance as they live together in Malibu.

Subsequently, Sophia confirmed in July 2018 that she was dating Caitlyn, previously known as Bruce Jenner.

However, in November 2020, Caitlyn's gal pal Sophia insisted their relationship is "not sexual" and they have never been romantically involved.

Sophia opened up about their partnership, insisting they are just business partners and that the former Keeping Up With The Kardashians star is like a parent figure.

Regarding Caitlyn's marital life, she was previously married to Chrystie Scott from 1972 to 1981.

She later married Linda Thompson from 1981 to 1986. Her last marriage was with Kris Jenner from 1991 to 2015.

Caitlyn has had six children from her marriages - Kylie Jenner, Kendall Jenner, Brody Jenner, Cassandra Marino, Brandon Jenner, and Burt Jenner

Who is Caitlyn Jenner?

Caitlyn Jenner was born on October 28, 1949, in Mount Kisco, New York.

Caitlyn is a well-known media personality and retired Olympic gold medal-winning decathlete.

She came out as a trans woman in April 2015, announcing a change in her name from William Bruce Jenner to Caitlyn Jenner.

After the transition, she starred in the reality TV series I am Cait.

As a result of her transition, she is a well-known transgender rights activist.

In an attempt to boost her political career, she ran as a replacement candidate in the 2021 California gubernatorial recall election.

However, she received only one percent of the vote, which made her place 13th among candidates that were seeking to replace Gavin Newsom.

What is Caitlyn Jenner's net worth?

According to Celebrity Net Worth, Caitlyn Jenner has an estimated net worth of approximately $100million, as of October 2022.

Her main source of wealth is said to be her career as a media personality.

She also earns income from brand endorsements and sponsorships.
